Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著寒冬漸深 許多事情發生了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的離去 名為「罪縛」的病
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥的死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尋回繭中的夢 得到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但礫卻仍身負著「罪縛」的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依舊繼續找尋著…無法尋回的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正太是明年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有大可以 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:27.56,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「別離·心的暗處·無法取代的事物」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河流的氣息真讓人喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有種懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是礫啦 說是會感冒 硬給我圍上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和礫分開了 不覺得寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會啊 才半個月而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒什麼精神在發呆的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許礫也感到寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了 又不是去什麼很遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是貴重品 別浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然祭典時會不夠用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在和客人打招呼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個翹頭髮的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣反而好像變成我們不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是光她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 在麵包店工作的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫落下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別讓人家受傷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 像個小鬼一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過跟小孩子在一起剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰湖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 大就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反相反 我們老是拜託你們幫忙帶小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該是我們過去打招呼才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為那件事的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和「Old Home」的關係反而變得疏遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼說話的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦 你才來這裏沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前曾發生過很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？綠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點忘了 這個還給礫 是向她借的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒變呢 礫那愛管閒事的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你真的什麼都不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前…我在這邊看到你們和礫交談…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有聽到傳言…礫和廢工場的冰湖一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私奔對吧？不要說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是礫自己的任性把冰湖牽扯進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰湖可是差點就死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫…礫不會做那麼過份的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不瞭解礫這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫傷害過誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫無論何時都很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使自己身陷痛苦 也總是用心體貼周圍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻一直都沒注意到那點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是空離去的時候 還是我成為「罪縛」的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都是礫更為痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻…總是依賴著礫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個文字…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫來接你了 好像很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫最近好像變得有點神經質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫很在意自己的離巢日遲遲未到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也覺得離巢日不來也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看著那麼痛苦的礫很難過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不希望礫離去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還在迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落下 你有鳥前來造訪 並得以尋回記憶的破片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但礫並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她必須獨自一人面對自身心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是相當艱辛的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫一直試圖畫出自己夢中的情境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖有見過一次 但卻不明白她所畫的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫好像也不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經沒剩下多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會是何時 並不為人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在這個冬天過去之後 應該就會有答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時 若礫的心中仍留有迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她便會繼續停留於此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以停留下來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極少數有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們已無法再被稱為「灰羽」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去翅膀與光輪 無法與人類和灰羽共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終年邁而死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣雖然安祥平穩 但卻是孤獨的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不 灰羽聯盟希望灰羽們都能平安的離巢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的礫在拒絕我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所說的話 總是讓礫的心變得更為頑固…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想助礫一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫明明一直都很痛苦 但卻隱藏著那樣的心情幫助著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次 我必須幫助她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救礫即是與其道別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫離開此處之後 也許就無法再度相見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有這個覺悟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 特地來接我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 買顏料順道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜這雪所賜 這傢伙大概也快不能騎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作如何？在努力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫呢？有在畫畫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在浪費顏料而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友 以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有說什麼過分的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她雖然嘴巴不饒人 但其實是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經五年了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我們兩個都是固執的脾氣 結果還是沒辦法合好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然好像不是什麼輕鬆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是得工作 才算是長大的灰羽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落下真好啊 工作是從下午開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱怨 別抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真好呢 總算找到了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傳染給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說要畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天由我來替孩子們做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最近不是一直在畫嗎 到底怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想讓她騎機車去圖書館幫我請假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託河魚去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？不行 會遲到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分鐘左右而已吧 有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家師傅就是不准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吧 反正也有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 河魚會載我去的 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 突然變冷了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你特地來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是落下嗎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就會出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來走動沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直坐著實在太悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要準備過年 偶爾也得散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 偶爾會想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個生命到底是從何而來的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 眠呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她感冒了 我是來幫她請假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書的化石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書的化石？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是什麼 雖然並不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以前在西邊森林深處曾有遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這就埋在那邊的石頭裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是因什麼力量變成石頭的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 有像圖案一樣的東西刻在上頭對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文字雖然也被稱為原始的繪畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是畫 大概是人的手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不瞭解礫這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就買桃子罐頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子對治感冒有效嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的 落下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的時候 不會想到桃子罐頭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是探病時的禮物…或是種習慣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著空虛的笑容 我們一同走著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時 礫都十分溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想讓任何人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想依賴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以礫笑著…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我沒有更早些注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與礫明明一直是最接近的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天不會到來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的過後還是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的日子 還有再接下來的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是今天的話就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就能一直和礫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠…是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼 總有一天都會終結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為現在就只是現在 所以這個瞬間…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會如此的寶貴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作了 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哭！我要幫助礫的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑啊 落下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠 長久以來謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有一天能遇到暗森的話 請幫我轉達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對不起 謝謝你」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…大概沒法到那邊去了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該做個了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:58.65,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wondering if we are true friends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:05.57,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}That distance cannot destroy and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:11.17,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wondering if you are lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:17.48,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}While waiting for my return
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:24.11,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Come,be one with me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:29.92,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Let us follow the path of light
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:36.29,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Mystery seeks to be understood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:42.23,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Some day we'll find truth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:47.87,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wondering just who I might be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:54.81,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Who I was and will become and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:10:00.37,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wondering if I can move on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:07.12,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Move into the world above
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:58.65,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我懷疑我們是否是摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:05.57,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那點距離不能破壞我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:11.17,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我懷疑你是否孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:17.48,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}當你等待著我歸來之時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:24.11,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來，與我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:29.92,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我們跟隨光的足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:36.29,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被發現秘密追隨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:42.23,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來日我們將找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:47.87,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我懷疑我是何物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:54.81,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我是誰 將來會變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:10:00.37,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我懷疑是否能繼續前行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:07.12,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}步入天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:55.28,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}なぜ 忘れたいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:23:01.16,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}ねえ 思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:14.03,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}あたたかい頬に降る 涙の願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.53,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}なぜ ふるえながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:25.09,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}今 求めあうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:31.72,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}君だけを何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:37.21,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}抱きしめたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}蒼い星の海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:49.47,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}波間に漂う羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:55.53,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}消えてゆく哀しみは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:24:00.91,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}明日への祈りなの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:06.16,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Blueflow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:55.28,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}為何想要忘卻？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:23:01.16,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}請回想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:14.03,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}那溫暖的臉頰上滑落而下的淚之請願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.53,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}為何你在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:25.09,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}現在尋求著何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:31.72,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}只有你無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:37.21,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}都想與你相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}蔚藍的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:49.47,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}波浪間漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:55.53,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}漸漸逝去的悲痛是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:24:00.91,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}向著明日的祈禱

